               Pushdown: enabled
               Remote Select: ?p ?o 
               Remote Sort Key:   DESC (?p)  ASC (?o)
               Remote Limit: LIMIT 3
(12 rows)

EXPLAIN (VERBOSE, COSTS OFF)
